==English==
===Etymology===
From [[tip]] + [[iceberg]].  Icebergs float in such a way as to have 90% of their mass below the surface of the water.

==={{idiom}}===
(only the) '''tip of the iceberg'''
#only the [[beginning]]; just a [[tiny]] [[indication]] of a larger possibility
#:''This is only the '''tip of the iceberg'''.  If this works, we can do much more.''

